div.p:
5. As CINCUNC you will, consistent with the security of forces under your command, inflict the maximum personnel and matériel losses on the forces of North Korea and Communist China operating within the geographic boundaries of Korea and waters adjacent thereto, in order to create conditions favorable to a settlement of the Korean conflict which would, as a minimum,
a.
Terminate hostilities under appropriate armistice arrangements;
b.
Establish the authority of ROK over all Korea south of a northern boundary so located as to facilitate, to the maximum extent possible, both administration and mil defense, and in no case south of 38th parallel;
c.
Provide for the withdrawal by appropriate stages of non-Korean armed forces from Korea;
d.
Permit the building of sufficient ROK mil power to deter or repel a renewed North Korean aggression.
